{"title":"春耕谣","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":2,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春耕谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凯歌高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风吹来冰雪消，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千条渠水系山腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金水灌地哗哗笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战胜旱魔凯歌高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学书记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大年初一积肥忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记背起金粪筐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人以他做榜样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春耕肥足粮满仓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔公社社员戴永清〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春灌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渠水湾湾流不断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似青龙游山川，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员舞锨引青龙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万顷麦田碧浪翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灌得红日落西海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灌得银月挂东天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灌得朝霞镶田埂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片歌声撒渠边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔公社社员恒　春〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缝春装"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二月里来好春光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎春花开四海香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓水抓肥抓工具，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙给大地缝春装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔彭波、胡洁〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪疙瘩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金疙瘩，银疙瘩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不如数九雪疙瘩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千车万担送到地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏收麦垛堆宝塔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔惠永珍〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送肥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你追我赶送肥料，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山歌随着鞭梢飞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱得心儿火一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱得地头肥成堆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔贺进才〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}